{"tid":566670,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"老豆包二奶 唔知點算好...","createTime":"2018-02-20T06:56:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-20T09:29:44.000Z","uid":92195,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ff258e5ee913762f053835bc434b18ef39657ff8","tid":566670,"uid":92195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T06:56:47.000Z","msg":"我老豆成日星期六日都唔番屋企瞓 前幾年就知佢成日去澳門賭 <br />\n<br />\n不過星期六日唔番黎瞓已經維持左年幾 我都有懷疑過佢係咪包二奶 有時又細細聲講電話 問佢去邊又唔講 老母已經好唔開心<br />\n<br />\n跟住到年初一 二又唔番黎屋企 冇同屋企人食開年飯 （我家姐啱啱嫁左出去 諗住新年齊齊整整食個飯）老母佢激到喊 好唔開心<br />\n<br />\n直到今日去廁所 老豆電話放左係廁所 我手痕撳下老豆we7 見到佢叫個女人做老婆    就知道一直既懷疑冇錯 個心真係好唔舒服 唔知應該點做好<br />\n<br />\n同老母講 老母一定好傷心 唔知承唔承受得到 唔知點算好"},{"pid":"3ba916b68b128f07a9ec7f0ca9a393799ae248a0","tid":566670,"uid":92420,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T06:59:08.000Z","msg":"我估你老母都知架啦，都無得點算，一係當唔知唔干涉，一係鬧你老豆一獲發洩"},{"pid":"46dafd9ba09aff5efa6ece3868138d6bab469fc6","tid":566670,"uid":80719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T07:00:21.000Z","msg":"take sides please"},{"pid":"9a2d7fb2c5126385818bdb5ee081f2cb3ecdcc6c","tid":566670,"uid":151534,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T07:10:21.000Z","msg":"叫佢比埋你屌囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6231ad17f706137908cad0136c1726855fecb685","tid":566670,"uid":165482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T07:14:36.000Z","msg":"你呀媽都心知肚明<br />\n陪多啲媽媽啦"},{"pid":"f925d8239ddb4e78c7ad1ce253ae9cadc1846004","tid":566670,"uid":65346,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T07:33:19.000Z","msg":"你老豆係公務員?"},{"pid":"8f84df499cf9e605bcf4a5373e38d08808a5a80c","tid":566670,"uid":146604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T07:35:42.00